'''Fleshglue''' was a cosmetic glue used to attach items such as jewels to skin. Primarily used by actors, it was also used by criminals to graft a good disguise.

During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], [[Alema Rar|Alema]] and [[Numa Rar]] removed their [[Adegan crystal/Legends|Adegan crystals]] from their [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsabers]] and, using fleshglue, they embedded them on the inside of their navels to disguise themselves as belly dancers.

